<emphasis id="8BD7037CCCCA6D5FF2C6187062DC9253" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="73">Lithocarpus congtroiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Ngoc &amp; Yahara 
<emphasis id="4DA8F05632203E20D6EB0B2ED557B999" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="73">A</emphasis>
twig with infructescence 
<emphasis id="E1A29D1853F5D52020256C5C6A09E96C" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="73">B</emphasis>
infructescence 
<emphasis id="97425AAC63ED2CEB2303882917F0DC87" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="73">C, D</emphasis>
leaves adaxially and abaxially, respectively 
<emphasis id="5370E4B282029C341D33F152AED85BA6" bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="73">E</emphasis>
